originalDescription: What room wouldnt benefit from the rich hues of gemstone colors? That beauty and elegance is now available in an array of gorgeous patterns with the Deepa collection. These stunning rugs capture the imagination and are created by artisans to fit in with any home decor. From stripes or geometric designs to abstract patterns and colors, the Deepa collection has a classic over-dyed and distressed look of age and history. Just the sight of one of these designs echoes memories from a different time or a foreign land. Despite their unique beauty and delicate design, these rugs are durable and kid-friendly, making them a welcome addition to any living room, dining room or bedroom. Theyre power-loomed and made from 100% polyester with medium pile height. If youre looking to add an elegant touch to your home or office, look no further. The Deepa collection will enhance the beauty of any room in your house.
newDescription: Bold & Fun! This colorful, oval rug, made of soft chenille blended with a hint of colored fabric, is the perfect accent rug for any playroom or bedroom.
